calculateThroughput

public static java.util.List<Throughput> calculateThroughput(double startTime,
                                                             double maxTS,
                                                             double thStep,
                                                             java.util.List<PacketInfo> packets)
Creates a list of throughput calculations for the time range and sampling window

Parameters:
startTime - Start time to begin throughput calculations
time - End time for throughput calculations
maxTS - The sampling window for each throughput point
packets - List of packets to calculate throughput on. This method assumes these packets are sorted by timestamp. Results are undefined for unsorted packet list.
